Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.54,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:44.54,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.08,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:48.17,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Echoes Act 3! {KILL DA HO MODE ACTIVATE}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.60,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Too bad for you...
