Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:06.06,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Run away if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:08.52,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,All I care about is getting my stuff back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:16.78,Main,Cop,0,0,0,,Check it out! \N Giorno actually fucked up! {Is "fucked up" appropriate? -Axel}
