Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:54.34,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Though the wound healed, \N your eye is always tearing up, hence the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:59.55,Main,Luca,0,0,0,,Here, have a seat.
