Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:14.86,Main,Luca,0,0,0,,Fifteen?! You're so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:20.74,Main,Luca,0,0,0,,You see, Giorno, there are three "don'ts" \N I find important for maintaining a good friendship. {The Japanese here is that there are three "U"s, and every point he brings up starts with a U-sound. Other than that, the translation for what he says is sound.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.07,Main,Luca,0,0,0,,Just three "don'ts".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:25.37,Main,Luca,0,0,0,,First, don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.45,Main,Luca,0,0,0,,Second, don't hold a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:30.37,Main,Luca,0,0,0,,And third, don't show disrespect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:33.79,Main,Luca,0,0,0,,Got that? \N Those are the three "don'ts" of friendship.
