Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.32,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mr. Luca...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:02.36,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I already paid my protection fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.32,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I'm out of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:05.20,Main,Luca,0,0,0,,To who, the security guards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:08.95,Main,Luca,0,0,0,,That has fuck-all to do with me!
